{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0\u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222720/extras/EN_title_1.png?t=1736778589\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore the ocean, from Epipelagic to Hadopelagic. From vibrant coral reefs to an abyss where light is absent. Craft sturdier diving suits and delve deeper down. Experience how it's like to swim through the ocean's different depth zones and discover secrets alongside the marine life. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222720/extras/shop_gif_scene_1.gif?t=1736778589\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222720/extras/shop_gif_scene_2.gif?t=1736778589\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222720/extras/shop_gif_scene_3.gif?t=1736778589\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0\u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222720/extras/EN_title_2.png?t=1736778589\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Through gathering resources and defeating enemies, gain the supplies to craft various different weapons. Combinded with the might of Bio-Embedded System , create a powerful weapon most suited for you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222720/extras/shop_gif_bullet_1.gif?t=1736778589\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" s